title: clearlag最新版怎么取消刷掉矿车
author: xiaosange
txt_content: config.yml都是英文的，眼花看不懂，麻烦大佬们帮个忙，clearlag最新版的在哪里设置可以关掉清理矿车的功能

replies.author: GuuWoo
replies.txt_content:
auto-removal:
  enabled: true
  broadcast-message: ''
  broadcast-removal: true
  autoremoval-interval: 460
  world-filter:
  # - this_world <-This world will be ignored during removal!
  boat: true
  falling-block: true
  experience-orb: true
  painting: false
  projectile: true
  item: true
  itemframe: false
  minecart: false
  primed-tnt: true

replies.author: xmdhs
replies.txt_content:
auto-removal:
  enabled: true
  broadcast-message: '&6[ClearLag] &aRemoved +RemoveAmount Entities!'
  broadcast-removal: true
  autoremoval-interval: 460
  world-filter:
  # - this_world <-This world will be ignored during removal!
  boat: true
  falling-block: true
  experience-orb: true
  painting: false

  item: true
